{"word":"ξυστόν","slug":"ξυστόν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ξυστόν</b></el> <el>(ξυστόν, οῦ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ξύω'><el>ξύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>the polished shaft</i> of a spear, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>generally, <i>a spear, lance</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}